; Coverage test for history.cc L488 (last_target = v_comm)
; Tests price conversion through a multi-hop path where the prices are
; defined in reverse direction (B->A, C->B) and we convert from A to C.
; The dijkstra path traversal must follow the reverse edges, exercising
; the branch where last_target is updated to v_comm instead of u_comm.

P 2024/01/01 B 2.00 A
P 2024/01/01 C 3.00 B

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    12.00 A
    Assets:Cash     -12.00 A

test bal -X C
                 C-2  Assets:Cash
                  C2  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
